'''敌敌畏'''（dichlorvos, DDVP<ref name="hazmap">{{Cite web|url=http://hazmap.nlm.nih.gov/category-details?id=248&table=copytblagents|title=Dichlorvos|date=August 2015|website=Haz-Map|publisher=U.S. National Library of Medicine|access-date=2015-10-13|archive-date=2019-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624221552/https://hazmap.nlm.nih.gov/category-details?id=248&table=copytblagents|dead-url=no}}</ref>）又稱'''二氯松'''，属于[[有机磷酸酯|有机磷酸酯]]类化合物，分子式C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>7</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>P，是一种常用的环境卫生[[杀虫剂|杀虫剂]]。敌敌畏自 1961 年以来一直是可商购的，并因其在城市水道中的流行以及其毒性远远超出昆虫而引起争议。<ref>{{cite journal |last1= Das |first1= Suchismita |name-list-style= vanc |title=A review of Dichlorvos toxicity in fish |journal=Current World Environment Journal |volume=8 |issue=1 |doi=10.12944/CWE.8.1.08 |year=2013 |doi-access=free}}</ref>敌敌畏自 1998 年起在欧盟被禁用。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pan-europe.info/old/Resources/Links/Banned_in_the_EU.pdf |title=Which Pesticides are Banned in Europe? |date=April 2008 |website=pan-europe.info |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210910080712/https://www.pan-europe.info/old/Resources/Links/Banned_in_the_EU.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==制备==
敌敌畏可由[[亚磷酸三甲酯|亚磷酸三甲酯]]和[[三氯乙醛|三氯乙醛]]反应或[[敌百虫|敌百虫]]脱氯化氢得到。1984 年，世界敌敌畏的年产量约为 4220 吨。其中约 300 吨是在西欧生产的。<ref name="Koch">Rainer Koch: ''Umweltchemikalien'', 3. Auflage (1995), VCH, Weinheim, ISBN 3-527-30061-9.</ref>

==性质==
敌敌畏是一种无色液体，<ref name="roempp">{{RömppOnline|ID=RD-04-01285|Name=Dichlorvos|Abruf=2014-02-07}}</ref> 有芳香气味。<ref name="GESTIS" />它的密度为 1.43 g·cm<sup>−3</sup><ref name="GESTIS">{{GESTIS|Name=Dichlorvos|ZVG=12500|CAS=62-73-7|Abruf=2017-01-10}}</ref>，熔点低于 −60 °C<ref name="GESTIS" />，沸点 140 °C，<ref name="GESTIS" />可溶于水。<ref name="GESTIS" />

== 用处==
敌敌畏对温室和室外作物中的蘑菇蝇、[[蚜虫|蚜虫]]、[[叶螨科|叶螨科]]、[[毛毛虫|毛毛虫]]、[[蓟马|蓟马]]和[[粉虱|粉虱]]有效。它还用于碾磨和谷物加工行业，并用于治疗动物和人类的各种[[寄生虫|寄生虫]]感染。它被喂给牲畜，以控制粪便中的[[肤蝇科|肤蝇科]]幼虫。它通过和摄入来对抗昆虫。它可作为[[气溶胶|气溶胶]]和可溶性浓缩物使用。它还以浸有杀虫剂的塑料形式，用于{{le|宠物跳蚤项圈|flea collar}}。敌敌畏自 1964 年以来一直可供家庭使用，并引起了一些担忧，部分原因是滥用。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Gillett JW, Harr JR, Lindstrom FT, Mount DA, St Clair AD, Weber LJ |title= Evaluation of human health hazards on use of dichlorvos (DDVP), especially in resin strips |journal= Residue Reviews |volume= 44 |pages= 115–59 |date= 1972 |pmid= 4576326 |doi= 10.1007/978-1-4615-8491-9_6 |isbn= 978-0-387-05863-4}}</ref>

==作用机制==
类似于其它有机磷酸酯杀虫剂，敌敌畏作用于[[乙酰胆碱酯酶|乙酰胆碱酯酶]]，它与昆虫的神经系统有关。有人已经提出了这也适用于高等动物的其他作用方式的证据。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Pancetti F, Olmos C, Dagnino-Subiabre A, Rozas C, Morales B |title= Noncholinesterase effects induced by organophosphate pesticides and their relationship to cognitive processes: implication for the action of acylpeptide hydrolase |journal= Journal of Toxicology and Environmental Health, Part B |volume= 10 |issue= 8 |pages= 623–30 |date= December 2007 |pmid= 18049927 |doi= 10.1080/10937400701436445 |citeseerx= 10.1.1.334.9406}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Booth ED, Jones E, Elliott BM |title= Review of the in vitro and in vivo genotoxicity of dichlorvos |journal= Regulatory Toxicology and Pharmacology |volume= 49 |issue= 3 |pages= 316–26 |date= December 2007 |pmid= 17936460 |doi= 10.1016/j.yrtph.2007.08.011}}</ref>据称它会破坏昆虫的[[DNA|DNA]]。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Espeland M, Irestedt M, Johanson KA, Akerlund M, Bergh JE, Källersjö M |title= Dichlorvos exposure impedes extraction and amplification of DNA from insects in museum collections |journal= Frontiers in Zoology |volume= 7 |pages= 2 |date= January 2010 |pmid= 20148102 |pmc= 2819063 |doi= 10.1186/1742-9994-7-2}}</ref>

==监管==
[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]已多次审查敌敌畏的安全数据。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Mennear JH |title= Dichlorvos: a regulatory conundrum |journal= Regulatory Toxicology and Pharmacology |volume= 27 |issue= 3 |pages= 265–72 |date= June 1998 |pmid= 9693077 |doi= 10.1006/rtph.1998.1217}}</ref> 1995 年，他们与供应商{{le|Amvac Chemical Corporation}}达成了一项自愿协议，该协议限制敌敌畏在许多（但不是全部）家庭用途、所有航空应用和其他用途中的使用。<ref>{{cite web |title=Dichlorvos (DDVP): Deletion of Certain Uses and Directions |url=https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/1995/04/19/95-9166/dichlorvos-ddvp-deletion-of-certain-uses-and-directions |publisher=U.S. Environmental Protection Agency: Office of Pesticide Programs |ref=Docket Control Number OPP-38511 |pages=19580–19581 |date=April 19, 1995 |quote=Docket Control Number OPP-38511 |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210910173934/https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/1995/04/19/95-9166/dichlorvos-ddvp-deletion-of-certain-uses-and-directions |dead-url=no }}</ref>2006 年、2008 年和 2010 年实施了额外的自愿取消。他们主要关注集中在急性和慢性毒性以及这种农药在城市水道中普遍存在的事实。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/12/us/pesticide-levels-in-waterways-have-dropped-reducing-the-risks-to-humans.html |title=Pesticide Levels in Waterways Have Dropped, Reducing the Risks to Humans |date=11 September 2014 |newspaper=The New York Times |last1=Wines |first1=Michael |name-list-style=vanc |accessdate=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712150222/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/12/us/pesticide-levels-in-waterways-have-dropped-reducing-the-risks-to-humans.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010 年的一项研究发现，尿液中有机磷代谢物浓度每增加 10 倍，儿童患[[注意力缺陷多动障碍|注意力缺陷多动障碍]]的几率就会增加 55% 至 72%。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/721892 |title=Organophosphate Pesticides Linked to ADHD |first=Megan |last=Brooks |name-list-style=vanc |date=May 17, 2010 |work=[[Medscape|Medscape]] |accessdate=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716024955/https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/721892 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors= Bouchard MF, Bellinger DC, Wright RO, Weisskopf MG |title= Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder and Urinary Metabolites of Organophosphate Pesticides |journal= Pediatrics |volume= 125 |issue= 6 |pages= e1270-7 |date= June 2010 |pmid= 20478945 |pmc= 3706632 |doi= 10.1542/peds.2009-3058 |url= |doi-access= free}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/slow-acting/ |title=Slow-Acting |magazine=[[Scientific_American|Scientific American]] |first=Paul |last=Raeburn |name-list-style=vanc |volume=295 |issue=2 |pages=26 |date=August 14, 2006 |doi=10.1038/scientificamerican0806-26 |doi-access=free |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104222054/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/slow-acting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==危险性==
工作场所的敌敌畏可以通过吸入、皮肤吸收、吞咽和眼睛接触而进入人体。{{le|职业安全与健康管理局|Occupational Safety and Health Administration}}（OSHA）已将工作场所敌敌畏暴露的法定限值（{{le|允许暴露限值|permissible exposure limit}}）设为 1 mg/m<sup>3</sup>（工作日8小时）。[[美国国家职业安全卫生研究所|美国国家职业安全卫生研究所]]（NIOSH）则将 8 小时工作日内的{{le|推荐暴露限值|recommended exposure limit}} (REL) 设为 1 mg/m<sup>3</sup>。在 100 mg/m<sup>3</sup>的浓度下，敌敌畏已达到{{le|立即危及生命或健康|immediately dangerous to life or health}}（IDLH）浓度。<ref name=":0" />

== 对人体的影响 ==
敌敌畏是一种{{le|乙酰胆碱酯酶抑制剂|acetylcholinesterase inhibitor}}。敌敌畏暴露的症状包括虚弱、头痛、胸闷、视力模糊、流涎、出汗、恶心、呕吐、腹泻、腹部痉挛、眼睛和皮肤刺激、{{le|瞳孔缩小|Miosis}}、眼痛、流鼻涕、[[喘鸣|喘鸣]]、{{le|喉痉挛|Laryngospasm}}、[[发绀|发绀]]、[[食欲不振|食欲不振]]、{{le|肌肉震颤|Fasciculation}}、麻痹、头晕、[[共济失调|共济失调]]、抽搐、[[低血压|低血压]]和[[心律不整|心律不整]]。<ref name=":0">{{PGCH|0202}}</ref>

敌敌畏也会影响 DNA 的生长，<ref>{{cite journal |title=Preferential Effect of Dichlorvos(Vapona) on Bacteria Deficient in DNA Polymerase |url=https://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/canres/33/3/458.full.pdf |journal=Cancer Research |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712145741/https://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/canres/33/3/458.full.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 并干扰人体神经系统。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nrdc.org/experts/mae-wu/big-court-win-public-health-pesticide-dichlorvos-bad-childrens-health |title=Big Court win for public health |website=NRDC |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712145744/https://www.nrdc.org/experts/mae-wu/big-court-win-public-health-pesticide-dichlorvos-bad-childrens-health |dead-url=no }}</ref>

